You are implementing a Blazor Web App for a veterinary clinic. The project is already scaffolded at `/tmp/sv-d728891e2ace4d79bba46d81aab2c0c8/VetClinic` with:
- .NET 11 preview, Interactive Server global mode, ASP.NET Core Identity with SQLite
- The template has Counter.razor, Weather.razor, Auth.razor demo pages that need to be REMOVED
